Logs Padhne ki Ninja Technique 🎯
  Rule 1: Sabse Pehle "Error:" ya "Cannot find" Dhundho
    Logs mein bahut saari lines hoti hain — unhe ignore karo. Sirf yeh pattern dhundho:
    Error:
    Cannot find
    Failed
    ENOENT (yeh matlab "file nahi mili")

  Rule 2: "Stack Trace" ko Ignore Karo (Shuru Mein)
    Yeh wali lines skip karo:
    at Function.Module._resolveFilename (node:internal/...)
    at Function.Module._load (node:internal/...)
    Yeh sirf "kahan se aaya error" bataata hai — kya hua nahi bataata. Beginner ke liye useless hai.
  Rule 3: Pehli aur Aakhri Line Dekho
    Error ki pehli meaningful line mein problem hoti hai:
    Error: Cannot find module '/usr/src/app/serve.js'  ← YEH DEKHO
